The paper deals with face image de-identification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques for facial attribute estimation and natural image synthesis, which falls under the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
